## Keys generated at first test run by `keys/generate-keys.mjs`.
## They are RSA 2048 keypairs used ONLY by the mock IdP fixture; never
## ship to production, never commit to git.
##
## Naming: `*.local.pem` is gitignored on purpose (per S5-1 iter 2 rule).
## CI generates the pair fresh per run.
*.local.pem
idp-private.pem
idp-public.pem
